(2, 7, 34, 'Diamond Sofa', 'PARKAVESDQUBED', '88.98', '70.87', '69.09', '163.00', '', '', '', '174.00', 'Y', '', '3', 'Y', 'Y', '960.00', 749.00, 1612.80, 1498.00, 2016.00, 1798.00, 30.00, 'China', 'Commerce, CA', 'Diamond Sofa', 'Park Ave', 'Desert Sand', 'Yes', 'Linen', 'Polydacron, Polyester Fibers', 'Desert Sand Linen Finish Cover', 'Hand-Crafted / Hand-Tufted by our Best Artisans', '69 Inch Tufted Headboard with Vintage Wing Accent', 'Low Profile Bed - Foundation or Box spring Required', 'Assembly Required', 'sofa.jpg', 'Park Avenue Queen Tufted Bed with Vintage Wing in Desert Sand Linen by Diamond Sofa', 'Park-Avenue-Queen-Tufted-Bed-with-Vintage-Wing-in-Desert-Sand-Linen-by-Diamond-Sofa', 'no', 100, 'The Park Ave Bed by Diamond Sofa is a hand crafted / hand tufted upholstered bed standing 69 inches tall.  The 12 inch frame includes four slats with center supports added into the cleats for structural integrity.  With its tufted headboard, vintage wing accents and wood feet finished in a rich medium walnut finish providing the backdrop for the Desert Sand Linen finish - creating this timeless addition to any bedroom\'s decor.  Bed is available in Queen, Cal king & Eastern King sizes.  Foundation or Box Spring is required.', 'complete', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
